title: Emily the Strange V1-4 and ebook collection
description:
Issues 1-4 of 'Emily the Strange V1' (Digital)
(Boring Issue, Lost Issue, Dark Issues, Rock Issue)
Dark Horse Comics, 2005-2007, 46-47 pages each
Written by Rob Reger, Brian Brooks, Jessica Gruner, Buffy Visick, Kitty Remington
Illustrated by Buzz Parker, Brian Brooks, Rob Reger, Mike Moon, Derek Fridolfs, Ryan Hill, Winston Smith

Volume 2 includes the original printed issues, which contain more pages and are in b&w, and the digital issues, which have fewer pages and have been colored.

Issue 1-4 of 'Emily the Strange V2'
(Death Issue, Fake Issue, Revenge Issue, Alone Issue)
Dark Horse Comics, 2007-2008, 31-34 pages (print), 23-26 pages (digital)
Written by Rob Reger, Jessica Gruner, Kitty Remington, Buzz Parker, Nicomi Turner, Matthew Weiss
Illustrated by Buzz Parker, Ryan Hill, Tim Biskup, Nicomi Turner, Jason Mecier, Turo Scissorhands, Fawn Gehweiler

Volume 3 includes the original printed issues and the digital trade paperback version. The original print versions are in b&w, the TPB is in color. Both contain pages that are not included on the other.

Issues 1-4 and the TPB of 'Emily the Strange V3 - The 13th Hour'
Dark Horse Comics, 2009-2010, 27-36 pages - TPB, 2011, 103 pages
Written by Rob Reger
Illustrated and Colored by Buzz Parker

Issues 1-4 of '(Emily the Strange) Emily and the Strangers' (Digital)
Dark Horse Comics, 2013, 22-25 pages
Written by Mariah Huehner, Rob Reger
Illustrated by Emily Ivie

Emily the Strange ebook collection
The Lost Days (2009)
Stranger and Stranger (2010)
Dark Times (2010)


This torrent does not contain the book Piece of Mind (2013), or the four Chronicle Books graphic novellas; Emily the Strange (2001), Emily's Secret Book of Strange (2003), Emily's Good Nightmares (2004), Emily's Seeing is Deceiving (2006).
